{
  "stem": "6257.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think they were particularly against his political views.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By the time I knew them, I don't think they were particularly rich.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He started, I think I remember, in their house, flat, rather, so bag fulls of some money, which we used to play with, which was a kind of-- I think that in the First World War, all this money suddenly became worthless, and they used to joke about it.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there were all these bag fulls of money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't think they-- but, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think that they felt that they were a rather superior family, yes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think there was that feeling, because my father-- yes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yes, I think that in the background, that they have-- they have come from some much more established family there in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It seemed so normal to me just, people coming and going, and perhaps arguing in the other room about things, and drinking vodka.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and in the summer, we used to go on holiday, that I remember, quite often, to the mountains, where my parents did some climbing, and in the [INAUDIBLE] Tatra Mountains.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But usually, there was also locally some youth camp of one of those political organizations.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they had some sort of context, and I used to get to know these young men, much younger than-- older than we were.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that probably my parents were unusually busy, because they were both working and profession, very, very busy and politically, whereas I think some of the children, most of the mothers were at home and not working.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that made it perhaps a little different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, this Polish young woman from the country.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
